1. activate venv/conda environment
2. in the parent directory 1d-neural-free-energy-training, run: pip install .
3. in config.py change these paths:
    local_checkpoint_path: str = (
        "path/to/where/you/want/the/models/to/be/saved/"
    )
    local_dataset_path: str = (
        "/path/to/dataset/"
    )
    local_datasplit_path: str = (
        "/path/to/package/cdft_1d_package/data_split/"
    )
4. python train_*.py 